<h2><strong>How Much Does Moving A Car From Alaska Cost?</strong></h2>
In Alaska, the cost of shipping a car can run from $1,500 to $4,500, while the average price across the country is between $500 and $1,500. The price of shipping a car to Alaska is contingent on the type of vehicle, the origin location, and the shipment season.
